 <link>https://www.ed.gov/news/press-releases/us-department-education-awards-nearly-270000-chardon-ohio-school-district-further-restore-safe-school-environment</link>
 <description>The U.S. Department of Education today announced it is awarding an additional $269,530 to Chardon Local School District in Chardon, Ohio, to help with ongoing recovery efforts following the 2012 shooting death of several students and injuries to others.</description>
